on my PR for re-enabling Cypress (https://cloud.cypress.io/projects/cfhedy/runs/13661/overview/1f347d56-91d8-4bcc-a3d8-70e501f17477?roarHideRunsWithDiffGroupsAndTags=1), `review-manager-dashboard` and `review-reviewer-dashboard` are failing because we show the “Metrics” tab by default now (see https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/62171), and the “Metrics” tab doesn’t have a “Run deployment” button

is this expected? @Liam Callanan @Udit
